
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<title>교보ebook</title>
<meta name="title" content="교보ebook">
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, width=device-width">
<meta name="robots" content="ALL">
<meta name="subject" content="교보ebook">
<meta name="author" content="교보ebook">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/eink.css">
<script type="text/javascript" src="../js/jquery-2.2.4.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../js/ui_eink.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="pagesub"> 
<!-- header container -->
<header id="header_container">
    <div class="header_fixed">
        <!-- header top -->
        <div class="header_top">
            <h1 class="hidden">교보문고 sam 7.8</h1>
            <!-- title -->
            <div class="top_area">
                <h2>교보 e캐시 간편결제</h2>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="btn_back">이전페이지</a>
            <!-- util -->
            <div class="util"> 
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#" class="btn_close">닫기</a></li>
                </ul> 
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- //header top -->
    </div>
</header>
<!-- //header container -->

<!-- body container -->
<div id="body_container">
    <main class="content">
        <!-- content --> 
        <section class="orderInfo_wrap">
            <div class="hd">
                <h3 class="tit">상품정보 (총 1건)</h3>
                <div class="rtl">
                    <p><span class="txt_rBox01">e-ink 스토어에서는 교보e캐시 결제만 가능합니다.</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="table_type01">
                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                    <col width="*" /> 
                    <col style="width: 130px" />
                    <col style="width: 128px" />
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>도서명</th>
                            <th>구매유형</th>
                            <th>판매가</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="prdTit"><a href="#">얼어 죽어도 아이스 아메리카노</a></td>
                            <td>구매</td>
                            <td><strong>9,900원</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="prdTit"><a href="#">얼어얼어얼어얼어얼어얼어얼어얼어얼어 죽어도 아이스 아메리카노</a></td>
                            <td>구매</td>
                            <td><strong>9,900원</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="prdTit"><a href="#">얼어 죽어도 아이스 아메리카노</a></td>
                            <td>구매</td>
                            <td><strong>9,900원</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <button type="button" class="btn_more">더보기 <em class="icon_arrow01_down">▼</em></button> 
            </div>
            <div class="totalPrice">
                <h3 class="hidden">결제 금액</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li class="price"><span class="col">결제금액</span> <span class="col"><strong>9,900원</strong></span></li>
                    <li><span class="col">결제 후 e캐시 잔여금액</span> <span class="col">9,900원</span></li>
                    <li><span class="col">현금영수증 신청 <a href="#" class="btn_tooltip">?</a></span> <span class="col"><button class="btn_open down">열기</button></span></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="cashSave_wrap">
                    <div class="row">
                        <span class="radio_box01">
                            <input type="radio" name="billType" id="bill01" value="1">
                            <label for="bill01">개인소득공제용</label>
                        </span>
                        <span class="radio_box01">
                            <input type="radio" name="billType" id="bill02" value="2">
                            <label for="bill02">사업자증빙용</label>
                        </span>
                        <span class="radio_box01">
                            <input type="radio" name="billType" id="bill03" value="3">
                            <label for="bill03">미신청</label>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="private">
                        <select name="" id="">
                            <option value=""></option>
                        </select>
                        <input type="text" class="input" title="휴대폰번호" placeholder="휴대폰 번호 '-' 제외하고 숫자만 입력해주세요">
                    </div>
                    <div class="business">
                        <input type="text" class="input" title="휴대폰번호" placeholder="사업자 번호를 '-' 제외하고 숫자만 입력해주세요">
                    </div>
                    <div class="receiptFalse">
                        <p>현금영수증을 신청하지 않습니다.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <script>
                    $(".totalPrice .btn_open").click(function(){
                        const tg = $(".totalPrice .cashSave_wrap");
                        if($(this).hasClass("up")){
                            $(this).removeClass("up");
                            $(this).addClass("down");
                            $(this).html("닫기");
                            tg.hide();
                        }else{
                            $(this).removeClass("down");
                            $(this).addClass("up");
                            $(this).html("열기");
                            tg.show();
                        }
                    });
                    $(".cashSave_wrap .row input[type=radio]").click(function(){
                        const idx = $(this).parent().index();
                        switch (idx) {
                            case 0:
                                $(".private").show();
                                $(".receiptFalse,.business").hide();
                                break;
                            case 1:
                                $(".business").show();
                                $(".private,.receiptFalse").hide();
                                break;
                            case 2:
                                $(".receiptFalse").show();
                                $(".private,.business").hide();
                                
                                break;
                        }
                    });
                </script>
            </div>
            <div class="agree_setting">
                <span class="check_box02">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="agree">
                    <label for="agree">구매조건 확인 및 결제진행 동의</label>
                </span>
                <a href="#" class="btn_info">교보e캐시 이용안내<span class="btn_tooltip">?</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="btn_area">
                <button type="button" class="btn_m02 submit">확인</button>
                <a href="#" class="btn_m02">취소</a>
            </div>
        </section>    
        <!-- //content -->
    </main>
</div>
<!-- //body container -->
</body>
</html>

